graph TD
    Start([Start]) --> PIN[Insert Card & Enter PIN]
    PIN --> CheckPIN{PIN Correct?}
    CheckPIN -- No --> Attempts{Attempts < 3?}
    Attempts -- Yes --> PIN
    Attempts -- No --> Block[Block Card & Exit]
    CheckPIN -- Yes --> ShowBal[Display Balance]
    ShowBal --> Input[Input Amount]
    Input --> Valid{Amount <= Balance?}
    Valid -- No --> Error1[Insufficient Funds]
    Valid -- Yes --> Multi{Multiple of 20?}
    Multi -- No --> Error2[Invalid Units]
    Multi -- Yes --> Limit{Under Daily Limit?}
    Limit -- No --> Error3[Limit Exceeded]
    Limit -- Yes --> Success[Dispense Cash & Print Receipt]
    Success --> Another{Another Transaction?}
    Error1 & Error2 & Error3 --> Another
    Another -- Yes --> ShowBal
    Another -- No --> End([End])
